Hello & thanks! Very good to hear from you again Niemand.

Thanks! Yes, at the moment I've managed to make 5 variants of core and booster tanks:

  1. First satellite launcher 8K71PS
  2. Vostok/Luna 8K72[K, L]
  3. Molniya/Voskhod/Polyot 8K78/11A57/11A59
  4. Soyuz 11A511
  5. Soyuz-FG 11A511FG

And 4 variants of Block I third stage:

  1. Molniya/Voskhod/Polyot (RD-0110)
  2. Soyuz (RD-0110)
  3. Soyuz-FG (RD-0110)
  4. Soyuz-2b (RD-0124)

Block E is in only variant (original Vostok and Luna) since I didn't wanted to expand too much the Vostok launcher family with Vostok-2, Vostok-2M etc., I've already cluttered the part list a lot.

I see some changes were made in terms of parts, Gemini went it's own way and to BDB, that's understandable. But it's a bit sad to see Venera lander disappear, what happened to it?
